    "vm_compute",
    "with"

    keywords: {

      built_in: BUILT_INS
    },
    contains: [
      hljs.QUOTE_STRING_MODE,
      hljs.COMMENT('\\(\\*', '\\*\\)'),
      hljs.C_NUMBER_MODE,
      {
        className: 'type',
        excludeBegin: true,
        begin: '\\|\\s*',
        end: '\\w+'
      },
      { // relevance booster
        begin: /[-=]>/
      }
    ]
  };

module.exports = coq;
